🔥 **Let’s pull a fresh, high-impact AI leader outreach list.**  

I'll identify **15-20 Alon-tier AI leaders** who:  
✅ Are **highly engaged** on LinkedIn (not just posting, but commenting & interacting).  
✅ Work in **AI automation, AI-driven business transformation, AI hiring, or AI-powered workflows.**  
✅ Are **likely to respond**—not ultra-famous like Altman, but influential.  

I'll get back to you with the **best names + personalized outreach plan.** Stay tuned. 🚀
